t is in a possible Downtrend. When the Triple EMA crosses ABOVE the Cumulative Delta then the asset is in a possible Uptrend.","updated":"2023-02-11T21:03:54.523Z","obfuscated":false,"likes":0,"usageScore":148,"shares":2072,"trendingScore":9,"sources":{"jdsDeltaOscillator.js":{"name":"jdsDeltaOscillator.js"}},"images":[],"author":"JDS"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"chartIndicator","link":"","caption":"Latter-day Trader: Previous Bar Retracement","authorId":207522,"indicators":["LDT - Previous Bar Retracement"],"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"This indicator draws a horizontal line on previous bars. You can specify where to draw the line. It defaults to 50% mark between the high and the low of that previous bar.\n\nIf you want to learn how to code custom indicators for Tradovate, search for \"Latter-day Trader\" on YouTube.\n\nAnd if you have found this or any of my other indicators useful, please consider sending a tip my way.  \n\nbuymeacoffee.com/latterdaytrader","id":"42649be8-1f0f-4b8a-92e9-ed09672601e6","obfuscated":false,"updated":"2021-09-04T22:02:18.527Z","likes":0,"shares":2052,"trendingScore":7,"usageScore":497,"sources":{"LDT_Previous_Bar_Retracement.js":{"name":"LDT_Previous_Bar_Retracement.js"}},"images":["2b46dd70-0259-4a30-9eb2-b9dd2cbb9bda"],"author":"LatterDayTrader"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"chartIndicator","link":"","caption":"Standard Deviation Channels","authorId":187183,"indicators":["Standard Deviation Channels"],"allowDirectLink":true,"id":"4bec7fc5-1b47-4f66-a240-27a558bc0f61","text":"This indicator is based on the Community Indicator: \"NOM Linear Regression Channel\".\n\nThis indicator plots the linear regression trendline and plots standard deviation lines above/below it.\n\nColor scheme based from NOM's popular VWAP bands.","obfuscated":false,"likes":0,"updated":"2021-06-01T15:13:41.560Z","usageScore":202,"shares":2047,"trendingScore":14,"sources":{"bnotb_standard_deviation_channels_v1.js":{"name":"bnotb_standard_deviation_channels_v