text":"A lower indicator that will calculate each individual candle by percent from 0 to 100.","id":"978f82a6-69a6-4f6b-a912-d7aa38d7220d","obfuscated":false,"updated":"2021-04-14T00:28:09.388Z","likes":0,"shares":663,"trendingScore":4,"usageScore":11,"sources":{"CandlePercentage.js":{"name":"CandlePercentage.js"}},"images":[],"author":"Proshot"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"workspace","caption":"High probability scalp NQ ES  rev. 3","indicators":[],"authorId":2661357,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"no channel, no cloud. Cadlestick reversions\n12 sec 3 sec 1 min\nKeep your eye on the 5 min- The algos apparently greatly respect the hull average (multicolored line) with aggressive moves when crossing. The hull is rspected across ALL time frames, including the 3 and 12 sec but especially the higher time frames","id":"4640315c-5f28-48f4-8859-43296e5f59bd","updated":"2024-08-15T15:13:55.014Z","likes":0,"shares":651,"trendingScore":15,"sources":{"High probability scalp NQ ES  rev. 3":{"name":"High probability scalp NQ ES  rev. 3.workspace.tradovate"}},"images":["528c9008-341b-44fe-a579-3e64563b40ff","69d7bdb9-1312-475f-958c-c0e86bdb4f52","8714ea09-f105-423f-89e5-ae408cf1e21e"],"author":"aaron matthews"},{"caption":"Smart-STRAT: Smart Structure by Javad","text":"Smart Structure by Javad (Smart-STRAT) is a real-time STRAT candle classifier and colorizer that repaints the body, wick, and border to show price-action states at a glance. It detects inside bars (1), directional 2 bars (2u/2d), and true outside bars (3) using strict breaks (equal highs/lows never count). The indicator tracks intra-bar order so failed 2s are marked correctly: a single-side break that reverses back inside without tagging the opposite side paints as a failed bullish or failed bearish 2; if the bar later takes both sides it upgrades to a 3, which always takes precedence. It also highlights next-bar failures after a prior outside bar. Colors are fully configurable (defaults: 1 = yellow, 3 = brown, failed bearish 2 = purple, failed bullish 2 = teal, 2s = standard up/down), giving a clean, faithful read of STRAT structure for intrabar and historical analysis.","link":"https://community.tradovate.com/t/smart-structure-by-javad-smart-strat/12388","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"abe71689-0f30-4fc9-993a-40ae1b51fdd6","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["Smart-STRAT"],"authorId":3476575,"likes":0,"updated":"2025-11-05T19:13:28.414Z","shares":650,"trendingScore":27,"usageScore":268,"sources":{"STRAT-Javad.js":{"name":"STRAT-Javad.js"}},"images":["c2d7c2aa-32b6-4d96-a325-799605384c13","e7d3ee05-939e-44fa-8236-6445be0489be"],"author":"Javad"},{"caption":"NukeGuy - Daily Candle","text":"NukeGuy – Daily Candle , brings the power of the daily timeframe directly onto any lower chart, plotting Highs, Lows, Open, Close (OCHL) in real-time with live ticks, so you never miss key levels. \n\nFully customizable, it lets you tweak candle colors, line styles, level highlights, padding, and OCHL label size and color, giving you a clean, precise view of daily structure on any timeframe. \n\nStay aligned with market flow and trade with clarity, confidence, and edge.","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"84171be1-aba5-4c43-af6e-c8efc5e56f43","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["NukeGuy - Daily Candle"],"authorId":4288627,"likes":0,"updated":"2025-10-07T21:29:43.716Z","shares":643,"trendingScore":13,"usageScore":336,"sources":{"NukeDAILYCANDLE.js":{"name":"NukeDAILYCANDLE.js"}},"images":["de3bc659-8107-4967-9a91-6ca15bdf11de"],"author":"NukeGuy"},{"caption":"Premarket Highlight Background","text":"This script will create and colour the zone from market close to market open during overnight session","updated":"2026-01-13T13:34:31.150Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"bb6bdf2a-4c3f-4c1d-b5be-68d743e1e682","entityType":"chartIndicator