indicators which is needed to make a true order flow big trades detector so I ended up building a synthetic \"tape\" instead.\nIt works by tracking all volume at price updates through a caching algorithm that can \"infer\" when big trades are made. It is incredibly accurate btw.\n\nPlease keep this in mind when using.\nAny chart refresh will wipe bubbles from inference that were recorded because it reloads the script runtime and wipes the memory. However, any \"applies\" made from playing around with the settings will not, so it's safe to tinker around with without resetting the inference point...however as you raise the threshold, the bubbles under the new threshold that were recorded will get wiped (the bubbles above the threshold are safe).\n\nFurther explanations can be found in the Tradovate forum and the settings features are explained in detail in the Order Flow Hub.","link":"https://community.tradovate.com/t/whale-scanner-big-trades-indicator/12597?u=unlimitidities","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"6c076150-ec62-4500-b355-516d0b94360f","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["WHALE Scanner"],"authorId":5094514,"likes":0,"updated":"2026-04-20T04:14:13.348Z","shares":329,"trendingScore":76,"usageScore":184,"sources":{"WHALEScanner.js":{"name":"WHALEScanner.js"}},"images":["1bdf66cd-da75-4c0a-bb12-9deabb1aa41c","a408a83e-1d66-4dd9-91e6-e9404d2fa782","f60872e0-403a-439f-872e-8d3b5f18d21f"],"author":"Unlimitidities"},{"caption":"Tiki Trend v1","authorId":113223,"indicators":["Tiki Trend"],"id":"b918e070-ba1a-4f2e-a541-70c723d92dba","text":"Tiki Trend v1","likes":0,"updated":"2020-07-22T17:39:24.159Z","usageScore":7,"shares":328,"trendingScore":-1,"sources":{"tikiTrend_v1":{"name":"tikiTrend_v1.js"}},"images":[],"author":"Ken Ko"},{"caption":"CVD","text":"Used indicators: p2f - Lonesome Cumulative Delta, Delta Divergence Signals","updated":"2025-05-23T07:28:02.126Z","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"entity