ce. Hold until happy with profit or when the 7 & 13 EMA crosses. \nVWAP is additional confluence when getting flat bottom rejections or wick tests.","updated":"2025-03-13T04:33:34.245Z","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","id":"04f38f34-deb7-4916-ac1d-8e2e92d23aaa","authorId":3959371,"likes":0,"usageScore":0,"shares":289,"trendingScore":9,"sources":{"Market Cheat Code":{"name":"Market Cheat Code.template.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":"JMac"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"colorScheme","module":"funCharts","caption":"gray Smooth mine","indicators":[],"authorId":440632,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"id":"2aed31bf-dbb3-4a63-a8a3-8cb160e93974","text":"Derived from dark color scheme.\nBackground: black. Labels: darkgray. Crosshair annotations: darkgray. Grid lines: black. High price: limegreen. Low price: crimson. Last price: gainsboro. Daily profile: darkslategray. Buy orders: limegreen. Sell orders: crimson.","updated":"2022-07-27T16:06:14.462Z","likes":0,"shares":288,"trendingScore":5,"sources":{"gray Smooth mine":{"name":"gray Smooth mine.colorScheme.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":" taniaVo"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","caption":"scalpmaster 1minute","indicators":[],"authorId":2704003,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"Used indicators: Stochastics, VWAP, SMA, Bollinger, RSI, Volume Profiles","id":"7e279577-aa5b-4fe0-9c6d-d299c609c27c","updated":"2024-06-24T21:08:46.339Z","likes":0,"shares":288,"trendingScore":4,"sources":{"scalpmaster 1minute":{"name":"scalpmaster 1minute.template.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":"giissas"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","caption":"SB Renko Channels","indicators":[],"authorId":1747189,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"Great for catching trends and staying in trades. The moving averages and Gann Lines provide incredible support/resistance points. The RSI is modeled from from the Traders D