s too weak (MACD < 3.5) or the other side isn't tired yet.\n\nThe Result: You stay flat, stay patient, and protect your capital.","updated":"2026-02-25T01:00:24.907Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"769d12c4-0219-4f58-94f7-8b8b4a796dea","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["ADX + MACD Quality Pro"],"authorId":2013127,"likes":0,"shares":56,"usageScore":15,"trendingScore":2,"sources":{"whippedcream.js":{"name":"whippedcream.js"}},"images":[],"author":"JulianGonzalez"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","caption":"JT 40 ticks-line chart","indicators":[],"authorId":9541,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"Used indicators: Exponential Moving Average, Bollinger Bands, Tiki IV Levels","id":"4392a2d1-50ed-4b7c-a97d-2b928b678769","updated":"2023-04-30T04:51:20.109Z","likes":0,"shares":55,"trendingScore":1,"sources":{"JT 40 ticks-line chart":{"name":"JT 40 ticks-line chart.template.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":"JayT"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","caption":"NQ","indicators":[],"authorId":2313740,"usageScore":0,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"Used indicators: SMA, NOM VWAP Bands, RSI","id":"6d062533-8c91-4989-af73-3319b69ef038","updated":"2024-04-05T06:23:00.491Z","likes":0,"shares":55,"trendingScore":0,"sources":{"NQ":{"name":"NQ.template.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":"Ruile Xiang"},{"caption":"Part 1: ADX Spread Momentum Signals","text":"This indicator is for the signals on momentum renko adx and shows the plot vs ma21","updated":"2025-08-25T02:16:32.368Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"0ddd96d8-af20-4a2e-91e2-9ee7e780d3d7","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["Average directional index Spread MA"],"authorId":2013127,"likes":0,"shares":55,"trendingScore":2,"usageScore":3,"sources":{"adxspread21ma.js":{"name":"adxspread21ma.js"}},"images":[],"author":"JulianGonzalez"