EMA AND the 20 SMA/EMA is below the 50 SMA/EMA. This indicates a strong bearish momentum within a long-term downtrend.\n\n    🟨 Yellow Bars (Neutral/Transition):\n    Displayed when the criteria for Red or Blue are not fully met. This usually occurs during trend transitions, sideways consolidations, or when the short-term momentum (20/50) contradicts the long-term bias (200).\n\nKey Features:\n\n    Trend Filter: Uses the 200-period average as a \"Institutional Filter\" to avoid trading against the primary trend.\n\n    Momentum Trigger: Uses the 20/50 crossover to capture mid-term trend shifts.\n\n    Fully Customizable: All periods and colors can be adjusted directly from the indicator settings menu.","updated":"2026-03-29T11:07:18.939Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"32279095-94a7-4caa-b17a-d0f3b1b70bc8","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["SMA 20-50-200 Trend Coloring"],"authorId":7146966,"likes":0,"shares":40,"trendingScore":3,"usageScore":15,"sources":{"TrendPainterPro.js":{"name":"TrendPainterPro.js"}},"images":[],"author":" Massimo"},{"caption":"VWAP SPS 2.0","text":"Used indicators: Tiki VWMA, Eman Overnight High Low (ONHL), SuperSessions, Tiki VWAP, Tiki Volume","updated":"2025-10-13T05:27:45.491Z","allowDirectLink":false,"entityType":"template","module":"funCharts","indicators":[],"id":"31e9a57d-c4c7-4842-b239-35de1f801a06","authorId":5013466,"likes":0,"usageScore":0,"hidden":false,"shares":40,"trendingScore":2,"sources":{"VWAP SPS 2.0":{"name":"VWAP SPS 2.0.template.tradovate"}},"images":[],"author":"SIR"},{"hidden":false,"entityType":"chartIndicator","link":"","caption":"VansBars","entitlement":false,"indicators":["Tiki Elder Impulse"],"authorId":1583537,"allowDirectLink":true,"text":"VansBars","id":"f5163c2a-693c-42b2-8689-bd90f4f9464d","updated":"2023-11-18T14:23:25.553Z","obfuscated":false,"likes":0,"usageScore":0,"shares":40,"trendingScore":0,"sources":{"VanBars":{"name":"VanBars"