oud fills, and real-time chart labels showing RSI value, delta, slope, distance-to-price, and bullish/bearish signal. One indicator, complete RSI intelligence.\n\nDetailed Description:\n\nMTForge RSI gives you everything you need from RSI in a single indicator — no clutter, no guesswork.\n\nThe lower panel shows a fully color-coded RSI line that tells you the trend state at a glance. Green means RSI is above 50 and rising, red means below 50 and falling, pink signals momentum fading above 50, and light green shows early recovery below 50. A 20-period moving average of RSI is overlaid and colored green or red depending on whether RSI is above or below it, giving you instant crossover awareness.\n\nA cloud fill between RSI and the 50 level makes it easy to see bullish and bearish zones. Overbought (70) and oversold (30) levels are drawn with the 50 midline changing color based on which zone RSI occupies — so","updated":"2026-04-22T19:41:58.229Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"f3d61044-050d-4757-8a03-852642832168","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["MTForge RSI (Lower Panel)"],"authorId":6515673,"likes":0,"shares":31,"trendingScore":5,"usageScore":45,"sources":{"MTForge_RSI_Lower.js":{"name":"MTForge_RSI_Lower.js"}},"images":["16f139fb-02b3-40da-86ee-bf5ee3e989b7"],"author":"NTForge"},{"caption":"OR Rotations + IB","text":"Inspired from Pax concepts","updated":"2026-03-20T16:05:09.545Z","link":"","allowDirectLink":true,"hidden":false,"id":"ad0f831d-a1d0-4fd0-9499-8ddc6d1ddc15","entityType":"chartIndicator","obfuscated":false,"entitlement":false,"indicators":["Opening Range and Initial Balance with Extensions"],"authorId":6008054,"likes":0,"shares":31,"trendingScore":4,"usageScore":13,"sources":{"SBJTrades_OR + IB's with Ladders + Extensions_ORs_IBs.js":{"name":"SBJTrades_OR + IB's with Ladders + Extensions_ORs_IBs.js"}},"images":[],"author":"SBJTrades"},{"caption":"PaperChaserv2","text":"Used indica